0And%20I%20think%20one%20of%20the%20opportunities%20in%20this%20is%20how%20do%20we%20create%20clarity%2C%20how%20do%20we%20help%20people%20understand%20that%20this%20work%20isn't%20about%20advantaging%20one%20group%20over%20the%20other.%20It's%20about%20creating%20fairness%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdarryl-page-came-out-of-retirement-chubb-chief-culture-officer-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705314421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1a77f6979d737182310b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdarryl-page-came-out-of-retirement-chubb-chief-culture-officer-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Darryl%20Page%20is%20chief%20culture%20officer%20at%20insurance%20giant%20Chubb%2C%20and%20focuses%20on%20diversity.%20Data%20shows%20DEI%20leads%20to%20better%20company%20performance%2C%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrose%40insider.com%20(Jos%C3%A9e%20Rose)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdarryl-page-came-out-of-retirement-chubb-chief-culture-officer-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prakhar%20creates%20history%2C%20slams%20unbeaten%20404%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705314398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106864321%2Cimgsize-41868.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fprakhar-chaturvedi-creates-history-with-unbeaten-404-in-cooch-behar-trophy-final%2Farticleshow%2F106864283.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka's%20Prakhar%20Chaturvedi%20has%20attained%20the%20unachievable%20feat%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20Cooch%20Behar%20Trophy%20final%20against%20Mumbai.%20The%20opening%20batter%20scripted%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20fi