outh-china-sea%2Farticleshow%2F106862870.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106862870.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Philippines%20will%20upgrade%20outposts%20in%20waters%20off%20its%20coast%20and%20acquire%20more%20ships%2C%20its%20military%20chief%20said%20Monday%2C%20as%20the%20country%20seeks%20to%20push%20back%20against%20China's%20growing%20assertiveness%20in%20the%20disputed%20South%20China%20Sea.%20Manila%20and%20Beijing%20have%20a%20long%20history%20of%20maritime%20territorial%20disputes%20in%20the%20waterway%2C%20but%20relations%20sharply%20deteriorated%20recently%20over%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%20involving%20vessels%20from%20both%20countries.%20Philippine%20military%20chief%20General%20Romeo%20Brawner%20said%20the%20country%20would%20develop%20%26quot%3Bthe%20islands%20and%20other%20features%26quot%3B%20it%20held.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-to-upgrade-outposts-in-disputed-south-china-sea%2Farticleshow%2F106862870.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-to-upgrade-outposts-in-disputed-south-china-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F106862870.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fphilippines-to-upgrade-outposts-in-disputed-south-china-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F106862870.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20A%20Decade%20Of%20Modi%20At%20The%20Helm%20-%20Changes%20In%20The%20Welfare%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20philosophical%20roots%20to%20its%20modern-day%20applications%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20social%20welfare%20has%20undergone%20a%20significant%20transformation%20over%20the%20years%2C%20evolving%20in%20response%20to%20societal%20changes%2C%20economic%20impacts%2C%20and%20historical%20contexts.%20Initially%2C%20the%20welfare%20state%20was%20conceived%20as%20a%20response%20to%20the%20palpable%20issues%20of%20poverty%20and%20social%20injustice.%20This%20early%20phase%20was%20characterized%20by%20a%20focus%20on%20providing%20basic%20assistance%20to%20the%20'deserving%20poor'%2C%20often%20underpinned%20by%20moral%20judgments%20about%20the%20behavior%20and%20worthiness%20of%20the%20recipients.%20The%20interventions%20were%20primarily%20reactive%2C%20addressing%20immediate%20manifestations%20of%20poverty%20without%20delving%20into%20the%20underlying%20causes.%20The%20poor%20law%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20was%20based%20on%20the%20premise%20that%20poverty%20was%20a%20result%20of%20individual%20failings%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20system%20that%20provided%20conditional%20assistance%20aimed%20at%20moral%20reformation%20and%20deterrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20philosophers%20like%20Thomas%20Hobbes%20and%20John%20Locke%20viewed%20the%20state%20primarily%20as%20a%20means%20of%20ensuring%20social%20order%20and%20protecting%20individual%20rights%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20emphasize%20the%20state's%20role%20in%20providing%20welfare.%20In%20contrast%2C%20later%20philosophers%20significantly%20expanded%20this%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20John%20Rawls'%20theory%20of%20justice%20introduced%20the%20idea%20that%20social%20and%20economic%20inequalities%20should%20be%20arranged%20to%20benefit%20the%20least%20advantaged%20members%20of%20society.%20This%20principle%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bdifference%20principle%2C%26quot%3B%20argued%20for%20a%20redistributive%20role%20of%20the%20welfare%20state.%20Rawls'%20contemporary%2C%20Robert%20Nozick%2C%20offered%20a%20libertarian%20critique%2C%20arguing%20that%20a%20minimal%20state%20focused%20on%20protecting%20individual%20rights%20was%20just%2C%20and%20any%20redistribution%20beyond%20that%20was%20morally%20impermissible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20the%20ideas%20of%20British%20economist%20William%20Beveridge%20and%20American%20President%20Franklin%20D.%20Roosevelt%20that%20shaped%20modern%20welfare%20states.%20Beveridge's%20report%20in%201942%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20UK's%20welfare%20state%20post-World%20War%20II%2C%20proposing%20social%20insurance%20and%20state%20responsibility%20for%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20welfare%20to%20combat%20what%20he%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bfive%20giants%26quot%3B%20-%20Want%2C%20Disease%2C%20Ignorance%2C%20Squalor%2C%20and%20Idleness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20welfare%20state%20evolved%20into%20a%20more%20sophisticated%20and%20comprehensive%20system%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20growing%20recognition%20that%20poverty%20and%20social%20issues%20were%20not%20just%20individual%20failings%20but%20were%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20economic%20and%20social%20structures.%20This%20shift%20was%20marked%20by%20a%20broader%2C%20more%20inclusive%20approach%20to%20social%20welfare.%20The%20focus%20expanded%20beyond%20mere%20poverty%20alleviation%20to%20improving%20overall%20living%20conditions%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20education%2C%20health%2C%20and%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20gaining%20independence%2C%20India%20faced%20significant%20challenges%20in%20public%20service%20delivery%20and%20social%20welfare.%20Despite%20the%20government's%20increased%20presence%20in%20social%20welfare%20and%20development%2C%20the%20delivery%20of%20basic%20services%20to%20the%20citizens%20was%20not%20efficient.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Ffeatured-insights%2Fasia-pacific%2Findias-path-from-poverty-to-empowerment%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20even%20in%202012%2C%20Indian%20households%20lacked%20access%20to%2046%25%20of%20the%20basic%20services%20they%20needed.%20This%20was%20due%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20corruption%2C%20inefficiencies%20in%20the%20public%20sector%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20infrastructure%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20service%20delivery%20is%20intrinsically%20linked%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20social%20welfare%2C%20as%20it%20is%20through%20the%20effective%20delivery%20of%20public%20services%20that%20a%20state%20actualizes%20its%20social%20welfare%20objectives.%20These%20services%2C%20which%20include%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20social%20security%2C%20housing%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20are%20fundamental%20to%20enhancing%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20well-being%20of%20the%20citizenry.%20The%20efficacy%2C%20accessibility%2C%20and%20quality%20of%20public%20service%20delivery%20directly%20impact%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20a%20society%20can%20address%20basic%20needs%2C%20reduce%20inequalities%2C%20and%20promote%20social%20justice.%20A%20well-functioning%20public%20service%20system%20ensures%20that%20social%20welfare%20policies%20are%20not%20just%20theoretical%20constructs%20but%20are%20translated%20into%20tangible%20benefits%20that%20reach%20all%20segments%20of%20the%20population%2C%20particularly%20the%20marginalized%20and%20vulnerable.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20public%20services%20is%20often%20a%20barometer%20of%20a%20country's%20commitment%20to%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20its%20social%20welfare%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20famously%20stated%20that%20for%20every%20rupee%20targeted%20towards%20welfare%20and%20poverty%20alleviation%2C%20only%20a%20fraction%2C%2015%20paise%2C%20reached%20the%20intended%20beneficiary.%20This%20statement%2C%20while%20not%20based%20on%20empirical%20data%2C%20highlighted%20the%20significant%20leakage%20in%20the%20system%20and%20the%20large%20operating%20costs%20and%20overheads%20of%20public%20service%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20made%20significant%20strides%20in%20transforming%20public%20service%20delivery%20and%20social%20welfare%20in%20India.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20initiatives%20has%20been%20the%20focus%20on%20financial%20inclusion%20and%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20(DBT)%2C%20which%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20ensuring%20that%20people%20have%20access%20to%20basic%20services%20with%20dignity.%20The%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Dhan%20Yojana%20(PMJDY)%2C%20a%20national%20mission%20for%20financial%20inclusion%2C%20has%20brought%20more%20than%2050%20crore%20people%20into%20the%20formal%20banking%20system%2C%20serving%20as%20the%20fulcrum%20of%20people-centric%20initiatives%20like%20DBT.%20The%20DBT%20model%20has%20been%20hailed%20as%20a%20'logistical%20marvel'%20by%20the%20IMF%20and%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20reducing%20leakages%20and%20curbing%20corruption.%20A%20G20%20report%20prepared%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20highlighted%20that%20India%20achieved%20its%20financial%20inclusion%20targets%20in%20just%20six%20years%2C%20a%20process%20that%20would%20otherwise%20have%20taken%2046%20years.%20The%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20country%20saved%20USD%2033%20billion%20through%20the%20DBT%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DBT%20model%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20ensuring%20that%20welfare%20reaches%20the%20needy%20without%20the%20humiliation%20of%20a%20'poverty%20parade'.%20By%20directly%20transferring%20funds%20to%20beneficiaries'%20accounts%2C%20the%20government%20has%20ensured%20transparency%20and%20dignity%20in%20welfare%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20health%20and%20education%20sectors%2C%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PMJAY)%20has%20been%20a%20game-changer.%20Launched%20in%202018%2C%20PMJAY%20provides%20a%20health%20cover%20of%20INR%20500%2C000%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20care.%20The%20programme%20aims%20to%20reach%20the%20bottom%2040%25%20of%20the%20all-India%20population%20based%20on%20measures%20of%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20significantly%20reformed%20the%20Indian%20education%20sector%2C%20with%20the%20landmark%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%20replacing%20the%2034-year-old%20education%20policy.%20This%20comprehensive%20policy%20revamps%20the%20entire%20educational%20structure%2C%20introducing%20a%20more%20flexible%20and%20holistic%205%2B3%2B3%2B4%20school%20system%20focused%20on%20foundational%20literacy%2C%20numeracy%2C%20and%20critical%20thinking.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20government%20rapidly%20expanded%20digital%20education%20initiatives%20like%20PM%20eVIDYA%20and%20the%20DIKSHA%20platform%2C%20enhancing%20accessibility%20and%20continuity%20of%20education.%20Vocational%20education%20and%20skill%20development%20have%20been%20emphasized%2C%20integrating%20practical%20skills%20into%20mainstream%20education%20and%20bolstering%20employability%20through%20initiatives%20like%20Skill%20India.%20In%20higher%20education%2C%20reforms%20like%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Commission%20of%20India%20(HECI)%20and%20the%20Institutes%20of%20Eminence%20(IoE)%20scheme%20are%20aimed%20at%20increasing%20autonomy%2C%20enhancing%20quality%2C%20and%20elevating%20global%20standing.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20government%20has%20fostered%20a%20culture%20of%20innovation%20through%20the%20Atal%20Innovation%20Mission%20and%20prioritized%20the%20internationalization%20of%20education%20with%20programs%20like%20'Study%20in%20India'.%20Central%20to%20these%20reforms%20is%20the%20commitment%20to%20equity%20and%20inclusion%2C%20striving%20to%20bridge%20gender%20and%20social%20gaps%2C%20ensuring%20education%20is%20more%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20across%20all%20levels.%20These%20transformative%20efforts%20mark%20a%20significant%20shift%20towards%20a%20more%20dynamic%2C%20skill-oriented%2C%20and%20globally%20aligned%20education%20system%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20also%20focused%20on%20improving%20access%20to%20basic%20necessities.%20The%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20aims%20to%20provide%20piped%20water%20to%20all%20of%20India's%20192%20million%20rural%20homes%20by%202024.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20made%20significant%20strides%20in%20sanitation%2C%20installing%20110%20million%20toilets%20between%202014%20and%202019%2C%20to%20provide%20sanitation%20for%20an%20estimated%20half%20a%20billion%20people.%20Access%20to%20electricity%20and%20clean%20fuel%20has%20also%20been%20a%20priority%2C%20with%20schemes%20like%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20providing%20subsidized%20cooking%20fuel%20to%20poor%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20has%20been%20achieved%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20in%20terms%20of%20social%20welfare.%20The%20possibilities%20are%20limitless%2C%20and%20the%20government%20continues%20to%20work%20towards%20ensuring%20that%20every%20citizen%20has%20access%20to%20basic%20services%20and%20opportunities.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20continue%20these%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20Indian%20citizen%20can%20live%20with%20dignity%20and%20access%20the%20opportunities%20they%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sequence%20of%20five%20columns%2C%20we%20will%20delve%20into%20the%20significant%20changes%20implemented%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20will%20discuss%20strategies%20for%20the%20incoming%20administration%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20it's%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20current%20party%20in%20power%20or%20a%20new%20one%2C%20to%20further%20enhance%20and%20build%20upon%20these%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705311780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fs9qt8aco_narendra-modi-road-show-pm-modi-road-show_625x300_29_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-decade-of-modi-at-the-helm-changes-in-the-welfare-state-4671987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20its%20philosophical%20roots%20to%20its%20modern-day%20applications%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20social%20welfare%20has%20undergone%20a%20significant%20transformation%20over%20the%20years%2C%20evolving%20in%20response%20to%20societal%20changes%2C%20economic%20impacts%2C%20and%20historical%20contexts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-decade-of-modi-at-the-helm-changes-in-the-welfare-state-4671987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-decade-of-modi-at-the-helm-changes-in-the-welfare-state-4671987%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-decade-of-modi-at-the-helm-changes-in-the-welfare-state-4671987%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jyotiraditya%20Scindia's%20%26quot%3BUnacceptable%26quot%3B%20Post%20After%20IndiGo%20Passenger%20Hits%20Pilot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAviation%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjyotiraditya-scindia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJyotiraditya%20Scindia%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20%26quot%3Bunruly%20behaviour%26quot%3B%20on%20board%20planes%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%20and%20every%20such%20incident%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20as%20strongly%20as%20existing%20legal%20provisions%20allow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Scindia%20also%20explained%20that%20the%20disorder%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20hr