0Pradesh%20is%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20receive%20government%20schemes%20that%20are%20being%20provided%20to%20the%20general%20population.%20With%20360%C2%B0%20profiling%20of%20households%2C%20any%20government%20employee%20household%20is%20automatically%20rejected%20for%20any%20state%20welfare%20schemes.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Anganwadi%20workers%2C%20they%20are%20treated%20as%20government%20employees%20and%20cannot%20get%20state%20welfare.%20At%20the%20same%20time%20they%20are%20treated%20as%20volunteers%20and%20do%20not%20get%20employee%20benefits.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20workers%20are%20fighting%20for%2C%20to%20not%20be%20excluded%20by%20the%20state%20in%20every%20aspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705311426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F03212236%2Fanganwadi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fanganwadi-worker-protest-maharashtra-poshan-tracker%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20for%20them%20is%20being%20increased%20with%20every%20new%20module%20added%20into%20unwieldy%20apps%2C%20the%20workers'%20wages%20have%20stagnated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fanganwadi-worker-protest-maharash