0world's%20most%20powerful%20social-media%20platform%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20new%20Sky%20documentary%20titled%20%26quot%3BZuckerberg%3A%20King%20of%20The%20Metaverse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20release%20comes%20one%20month%20before%20Facebook's%2020th%20birthday%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20academic%2C%20the%20extraordinary%20arc%20of%20Zuckerberg's%20life%20in%20the%20two%20decades%20since%202003%20%E2%80%94%20laid%20bare%20in%20the%20documentary%20%E2%80%94%20has%20posed%20a%20vital%20question%3A%20do%20we%20really%20know%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227371%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516df11f5d0bb0019e5ae00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224916%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20is%20CEO%20of%20Facebook%20owner%20Meta.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20creator%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzuckerbergfiles.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZuckerberg%20Files%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20launched%20in%202013%2C%20Marquette%20University's%20privacy%20and%20data%20ethics%20scholar%2C%20Michael%20Zimmer%2C%20has%20made%20it%20his%20mission%20to%20answer%20that%20question%20by%20obsessively%20documenting%20everything%20Zuckerberg%20has%20said%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20three%20billion%20of%20the%20world's%20eight%20billion%20people%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta-owned%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0be%20it%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20or%20Threads%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Zimmer's%20reason%20for%20doing%20this%20is%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Zuckerberg%20Files%20came%20out%20of%20a%20project%20where%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20how%20Zuckerberg%20talks%20about%20privacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimmer%20explained%20in%20the%20documentary.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20started%20collecting%20blog%20posts%20and%20speeches%20or%20interviews%20he%20gave%20around%20privacy%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20digital%20archive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20quickly%20became%20much%20more%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-mark-zuckerberg-privacy-vision-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillionaire's%20views%20on%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Zimmer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20became%20fascinated%20with%20how%20the%20CEO%20spoke%20about%20why%20Facebook%20existed%2C%20his%20response%20to%20%26quot%3Bpushback%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20language%20when%20controversies%20would%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20of%20being%20able%20to%20really%20track%20how%20his%20discourse%20changes%2C%20the%20language%20he%20uses%20both%20on-script%20and%20off-script%20I%20found%20really%20intriguing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZimmer%20thinks%20the%20exhaustive%20project%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Breally%20insightful%26quot%3B%20in%20helping%20track%20the%20maturity%20of%20both%20Zuckerberg%20and%20his%20company.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20it's%20hard%20for%20him%20to%20say%20he%20really%20knows%20the%20guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20I%20look%20into%20his%20soul%2C%20can%20I%20understand%20Zuckerberg%3F%26quot%3B%20Zimmer%20asked%20himself.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20understandable.%20As%20the%20documentary%20depicts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mark-zuckerberg-meta-facebook-ceo-layoffs-profit-cage-match-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZuckerberg's%20life%20has%20undergone%20transformation%20after%20transformation.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20the%20young%20Zuckerberg%20who%20is%20a%20visionary%2C%20as%20David%20Kirkpatrick%2C%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Facebook%20Effect%2C%26