ndian%20cricket%20fan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20is%20the%20highest%20run-getter%20in%20T20Is.%20In%20116%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%204%2C037%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2052.42%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20138.20.%20He%20has%20scored%20a%20century%20and%2037%20fifties%20and%20his%20best%20score%20is%20122*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20also%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20with%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20shot%20selection.%20Rohit%20attempted%20to%20dance%20down%20the%20track%20for%20an%20aggressive%20shot%2C%20but%20was%20cleaned%20up%20by%20Fazalhaq%20Farooqi%20for%20a%20golden%20duck%2C%20his%20second%20duck%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20extremely%20surprising%20the%20way%20Rohit%20got%20out.%20He%20was%20playing%20just%20his%20first%20ball.%20He%20does%20not%20play%20such%20shots.%20The%20ball%20went%20and%20hit%20his%20stumps.%20He%20got%20run%20out%20in%20the%20last%20match%20and%20was%20bowled%20for%20zero%20in%20this%20match.%20He%20has%20not%20scored%20a%20single%20run%20in%20this%20series%20thus%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20said%20that%20Rohit%20will%20have%20to%20score%20some%20runs%20in%20IPL%202024%20and%20Men%20in%20Blue%20need%20the%20starts%20he%20used%20to%20provide%20during%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20last%20year%2C%20during%20which%20he%20scored%20597%20runs%20in%2011%20matches%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20125.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRun-out%20was%20not%20his%20mistake%20but%20the%20shot%20selection%20was.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20form%20and%20ability.%20However%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20be%20in%20form%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20I%20feel%20he%20will%20bat%20like%20this%20only.%20We%20need%2038-40%2C%20the%20runs%20he%20was%20scoring%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20from%20his%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20field%20first%20and%20troubled%20Afghanistan%20with%20frequent%20wickets.%20Gulbadin%20Naib%20(57%20in%2035%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20continued%20to%20play%20unbothered%2C%20despite%20wickets%20falling%20at%20the%20other%20end%20and%20made%20an%20attacking%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort%20cameos%20from%20Najibullah%20Zadran%20(23%20in%2021%20balls%20with%20a%20boundary%20and%20two%20sixes)%2C%20Karim%20Janat%20(20%20in%2010%20balls%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Mujeeb%20ur%20Rahman%20(21%20in%20nine%20balls%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20powered%20Afghanistan%20to%20172%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacer%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20(3%2F32)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India%2C%20while%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20(2%2F39)%20and%20Axar%20(2%2F17)%20also%20bowled%20well%20to%20restrict%20Afghanistan's%20run%20flow.%20Shivam%20Dube%20also%20took%201%2F36%20in%20his%20three%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chase%20of%20173%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20once%20again%20out%20for%20a%20duck.%20But%20a%20returning%20Virat%20Kohli%20(29%20in%2016%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours)%20played%20with%20a%20refreshing%20attacking%20intent%20and%20formed%20a%2057-run%20stand%20with%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal.%20Following%20Virat's%20dismissal%2C%20Yashasvi%20(68%20in%2034%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(63*%20in%2032%20balls%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20demolished%20the%20Afghanistan%20bowling%20line-up%20with%20their%20hitting%2C%20putting%20up%20a%2092-run%20partnership%20in%20just%2042%20balls.%20Rinku%20Singh%20(9*)%20and%20Shivam%20finished%20off%20things%20to%20give%20India%20a%20six-wicket%20win%20and%20a%20series%20win%20by%202-0%2C%20with%20one%20game%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarim%20Janat%20(2%2F13)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20Afghanistan.%20Axar%20Patel%20was%20t