ed%20by%20the%20department%20during%20the%20previous%20year%202021-22%2C%20which%20was%20Rs%205%2C152.6%20crore%20of%20its%201.23%20lakh%20crore%20allocation%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20surrendered%20Rs%2023%2C824.53%20crore%20in%202020-21%2C%20Rs%2034%2C517.7%20crore%20in%202019-20%2C%20and%20Rs%2021%2C043.75%20crore%20in%202018-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Agriculture%20has%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20avoid%20this%20practice%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20fund%20surrender%20is%20mainly%20due%20to%20less%20requirement%20in%20specific%20components.%20The%20report%20also%20notes%20a%20marginal%20reduction%20in%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20total%20allocation%20for%20the%20current%20financial%20year%2C%20possibly%20reflecting%20the%20non-utilisation%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20and%20Education%2C%20which%20also%20comes%20under%20the%20ministry%2C%20has%20surrendered%20Rs%209%20lakh%20of%20its%20total%20allocation%20of%20Rs%208%2C658.91%20crore%20in%202022-23%2C%20Rs%201.81%20crore%20in%202021-22%2C%20Rs%20600%20crore%20in%202020-21%2C%20Rs%20232.62%20crore%20in%202019-20%20and%20Rs%207.9%20crore%20in%202018-2019%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202018-19%2C%20the%20collective%20budget%20of%20the%20two%20departments%20under%20the%20Agriculture%20Ministry%20witnessed%20an%20increase%20from%20Rs%2054%2C000%20crore%20(constituting%202.3%25%20of%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20total%20budget%20of%20Rs%2024.42%20lakh%20crore)%20in%202018-19%20to%20Rs%201.32%20lakh%20crore%20(equivalent%20to%203.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20Rs%2039.44%20lakh%20crore%20in%202022-23).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20has%20been%20allocated%20an%20annual%20budget%20ranging%20from%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20to%20Rs%2075%2C000%20crore%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20However%2C%20for%20the%20current%20financial%20year%202023-24%2C%20the%20government%20has%20slightly%20reduced%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20total%20allocation%20to%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20crore%20from%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20Rs%201.32%20lakh%20crore%2C%20potentially%20due%20to%20the%20non-utilisation%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705309249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01132506%2FAgriculture_main.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fagri-ministry-didnt-utilise-its-increased-budget-surrendered-rs-1-trillion-in-last-5-years-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20last%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20surrendered%20around%20Rs%2021%2C000%20crore%20out%20of%20its%20annual%20allocation%20of%20Rs%201.24%20trillion%2C%20'The%20Indian%20Express'%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fagri-ministry-didnt-utilise-its-increased-budget-surrendered-rs-1-trillion-in-last-5-years-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goa%20murder%3A%20Court%20extends%20B'luru%20CEO's%20police%20custody%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705309125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106861144%2Cimgsize-662326.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fgoa-court-extends-police-custody-of-ceo-suchana-seth-by-five-days%2Farticleshow%2F106860777.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Goa%20court%20on%20Monday%20extended%20the%20police%20custody%20of%20Suchana%20Seth%2C%20CEO%20of%20a%20startup%2C%20by%20an%20additional%20five%20days.%20Suchana%20is%20facing%20a%20probe%20for%20the%20allegedly%20killing%20her%20four-year-old%20son.%20She%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20Goa%20Children's%20Court%20after%20her%