n%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Boeing%20turned%20to%20leaders%20out%20of%20the%20mold%20of%20legendary%20General%20Electric%20Co.%20CEO%20Jack%20Welch%2C%20and%20the%20financial%20targets%20and%20metrics%20this%20crop%20of%20executives%20put%20in%20place%20tore%20away%20many%20of%20Boeing's%20traditional%20practices.%20Calhoun%2C%20who%20took%20over%20early%20in%202020%2C%20previously%20worked%20at%20GE%2C%20before%20spending%20half%20a%20decade%20at%20investment%20firm%20Blackstone%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20made%20it%20a%20great%20company%20is%2C%20it%20built%20the%20greatest%20airplanes%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Adams%2C%20a%20former%20president%20of%20aero%20engine%20maker%20Pratt%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20people%20needed%20their%20product.%20And%20they%20had%20long-term%20sustainability.%20When%20they%20went%20to%20the%20mode%20of%20trying%20to%20optimize%20financially%2C%20they%20lost%20the%20DNA%20that%20made%20them%20a%20great%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F1toi8leg_boeing-share-bloomberg-graph_625x300_15_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20executives%20say%20that%20under%20Calhoun%2C%20Boeing%20has%20dramatically%20scaled%20back%20detailed%20operating%20reviews%20that%20were%20commonplace%20previously%20and%20undertook%20deep%20dives%20into%20engineering%2C%20quality%2C%20finance%20and%20human%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalhoun's%20shifting%20of%20executive%20committee%20gatherings%20from%20monthly%20to%20quarterly%20sessions%20also%20reflect%20his%20informal%20management%20style%2C%20say%20others%20who've%20witnessed%20his%20leadership.%20He%20has%20little%20patience%20for%20rehearsed%20presentations%2C%20instead%20peppering%20executives%20with%20impromptu%20phone%20calls%2C%20and%20bypassing%20them%20to%20go%20straight%20to%20engineers%2C%20as%20he%20did%20in%20the%20Alaska%20Air%20accident%20aftermath%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20didn't%20make%20Calhoun%20available%20for%20an%20interview%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Boeing%2C%20the%20financial%20cost%20of%20the%20737%20Max%209%20grounding%20will%20probably%20be%20far%20outweighed%20by%20the%20longstanding%20loss%20of%20confidence%20that%20ripples%20from%20it%2C%20said%20one%20former%20senior%20Boeing%20executive%2C%20who%20also%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified.%20While%20the%20company%20digs%20into%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20its%20quality%20woes%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20empowering%20employees%20rather%20than%20treating%20them%20like%20an%20expense%2C%20the%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20lost%20the%20DNA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20latest%20mishap%20tarnished%20the%20737's%20reputation%2C%20Boeing%20was%20hugely%20reliant%20on%20the%20single-aisle%20program%20to%20pull%20the%20company%20along.%20Of%20the%20528%20aircraft%20delivered%20by%20Boeing%20last%20year%2C%20396%20were%20737%20models%2C%20underscoring%20just%20how%20crucial%20it%20remains.%20And%20cashflow%20from%20the%20737%20keeps%20the%20entire%20company%20humming%20along%2C%20from%20widebodies%20to%20space%20programs%20to%20defense%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20analysts%20say%20Boeing%20would%20be%20well%20advised%20to%20shift%20strategy%20and%20messaging%20away%20from%20the%20cash%20that%20for%20years%20has%20been%20Boeing's%20siren%20call%20to%20Wall%20Street%20-%20particularly%20as%20its%20failings%20are%20being%20examined%20under%20the%20political%20microscope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoeing%20has%20to%20be%20careful%20on%20pounding%20the%20table%20on%20free%20cash%20while%20managing%20a%20public%