6.21%20lakh%20square%20kilometres)%20last%20month%20after%20the%20Department%20of%20State%20(DOS)%20added%20six%20regions'%20submerged%20offshore%20areas%2C%20called%20extended%20continental%20shelf%20(ECS)%2C%20to%20the%20total%20landmass%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20ECS%20is%20the%20area%20of%20the%20continental%20shelf%20that%20is%20under%20shallow%20water%2C%20beyond%20200%20nautical%20miles.%20The%20largest%20ECS%20area%20for%20the%20US%20is%20the%20Arctic%20-%20350%20miles%20(612%20km)%20to%20the%20north%20and%20more%20than%20680%20miles%20(1%2C094%20km)%20in%20the%20western%20region%20-%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20USGS%2C%20it%20is%20an%20important%20maritime%20zone%20that%20holds%20many%20resources%20and%20vital%20habitats%20for%20marine%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20that%20America's%20ECS%20includes%20six%20other%20regions%3A%20The%20Atlantic%20east%20coast%2C%20the%20Pacific%20west%20coast%2C%20the%20Bering%20Sea%2C%20the%20Mariana%20Islands%20and%20two%20portions%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20other%20countries%2C%20the%20United%20States%20has%20rights%20under%20international%20law%20to%20conserve%20and%20manage%20the%20resources%20and%20vital%20habitats%20on%20and%20under%20its%20ECS%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20State%20Department%20said%20in%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20area%20added%20to%20the%20US%20territory%20is%20nearly%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilson%20Centre%2C%20a%20think%20tank%20based%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20said%20that%20ECS%20extension%20has%20major%20implications%20for%20US's%20efforts%20to%20secure%20its%20territorial%20rights%20in%20the%20Arctic%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20long%20been%20clear%20that%20the%20United%20States%20has%20major%20economic%20interests%20in%20undersea%20territory%20rich%20in%20oil%2C%20natural%20gas%2C%20minerals%20and%20sea%20life%20to%20which%20it%20has%20sovereign%20rights%20under%20the%20law%20of%20the%20sea%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20Convention%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20think%20tank%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F01%2F12%2Fusa-growth-extended-continental-shelf-20107833%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilson%20Centre%20also%20said%20that%20the%20US%20has%20the%20largest%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20which%20helps%20it%20safeguard%20its%20sovereign%20rights%20to%20areas%20submerged%20under%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20an%20important%20milestone%20reflecting%20US%20engagement%20with%20the%20law%20of%20the%20sea%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20and%20as%20an%20aspect%20of%20advancing%20major%20US%20interests%20in%20the%20Arctic%20and%20other%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Wilson%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extension%20of%20the%20ECS%20is%20based%20on%20the%20analysis%20of%20data%20collected%20by%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20(NOAA)%20and%20USGS.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705308600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fnkk22sq8_us-generic-650_650x400_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-quietly-grew-400-000-square-miles-nearly-twice-the-size-of-spain-4866412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20has%20the%20largest%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20which%20helps%20it%20safeguard%20its%20sovereign%20rights%20to%20areas%20submerged%20under%20water.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-quietly-grew-400-000-square-miles-nearly-twice-the-size-of-spain-4866412%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject