0front%2C%20continuity%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20watchword.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20established%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%2C%20nurtured%20by%20President%20Tsai%20Ing-wen%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Vice%20President%20Bi%20khim%20Hsiao.%20Her%20esteemed%20record%20as%20former%20ambassador%20to%20the%20US%20inspires%20confidence%20in%20maintaining%20strong%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20cross-strait%20relations%20with%20China%20face%20a%20potential%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20President%20and%20Vice%20President%20openly%20supporting%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20independence%20in%20the%20past%2C%20China%20perceives%20them%20as%20a%20united%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fpage%2F202311%2F1302696.shtml%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cindependence%20duo%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20stance%20may%20trigger%20harsh%20responses%2C%20from%20further%20curtailing%20trade%20via%20terminating%20the%20free%20trade%20agreement%20to%20heightened%20military%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20forward%20requires%20navigating%20a%20delicate%20balance%20of%20upholding%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20values%20while%20recognising%20the%20complex%20geopolitical%20realities.%20The%20future%20of%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20cross-strait%20relationship%20hinges%20on%20how%20well%20this%20balance%20is%20upheld.%20The%20governing%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20will%20be%20judged%20on%20how%20they%20walk%20the%20tightrope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%E2%80%99s%20emergence%20may%20seem%20to%20add%20another%20layer%20of%20complexity%2C%20with%20its%20potentially%20divergent%20views%20on%20cross-strait%20policy.%20The%20party%20believes%20demonstrating%20goodwill%20can%20lower%20the%20temperature%20and%20avoid%20harsher%20measures%20like%20trade%20restrictions%20or%20military%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20unlike%20the%20Kuomintang%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D