D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fstrength-of-indian-army-lies-in-its-apolitical-character-western-command-chief-2847937%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Western%20Command%20of%20army%20noted%20significant%20acts%20of%20valour%20by%20Indian%20army%20personnel%20in%20the%20past%20as%20important%20to%20seek%20inspiration%20from.%20He%20noted%20that%20in%20warfare%20in%20the%20future%2C%20for%20all%20the%20talk%20of%20advancements%20in%20technology%2C%20the%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20role%20will%20remain%20crucial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20positions%2C%20all%20ranks%20also%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20professional%20development%20and%20physical%20fitness%20because%20the%20next%20battle%20will%20be%20high-tech%2C%20and%20it%20will%20also%20be%20in%20difficult%20terrain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20spoke%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Enaam%2C%20namak%2C%20nishan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20name%2C%20salt%2C%20symbol%20%E2%80%93%20as%20values%20central%20to%20what%20soldiers%20stand%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20Gen%20Katiyar%20took%20over%20this%20present%20post%20in%20July%2C%202023.%20Before%20this%2C%20he%20was%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Military%20operations%20(DGMO)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20General%20Katiyar%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Ati%20Vishisht%20Seva%20Medal%20for%20distinguished%20service%20in%202021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArmy%20Day%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%2076th%20Army%20Day.%20January%2015%20is%20observed%20as%20Army%20Day%2C%20each%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20commemorates%20the%20day%20India%E2%80%99s%20Army%20was%20detangled%20from%20the%20British.%20On%2015%