%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20you%20gotta%20get%20up%2C%20you%20gotta%20vote%2C%20because%20it%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20anything%20but%20taking%20our%20nation%20back%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20biggest%20thing%20there%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20caucuses%20are%20in-person%20meetings%20where%20registered%20Republican%20voters%20gather%20in%20their%20local%20precincts%20and%20discuss%20various%20candidates.%20At%20the%20end%2C%20each%20casts%20a%20secret%20ballot%20for%20their%20preferred%20presidential%20hopeful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIowa%20Republicans%20are%20to%20meet%20on%20Monday%20evening%20when%20the%20state%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20still%20caught%20in%20subzero%20wind%20chills%20following%20a%20blizzard%20that%20struck%20the%20region%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Remote%20voting%20is%20not%20available%20for%20the%20Republican%20caucus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Weather%20Service%20issued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weather.gov%2Fwwamap%2Fwwatxtget.php%3Fcwa%3Ddmx%26wwa%3Dall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20warnings%20and%20advisories%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20describing%20the%20chills%20as%20%26quot%3Blife-threatening%26quot%3B%20and%20urging%20people%20to%20limit%20their%20time%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20freezing%20winds%20are%20expected%20to%20last%20until%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20the%20clear%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20with%20former%20US%20ambassador%20Nikki%20Haley%20and%20Florida%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20vying%20for%20second%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Trump%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-worth-it-sick-vote-iowa-caucus-pass-away-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fd