4%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-3-1705068511-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-3-1705068511-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-3-1705068511-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-3-1705068511-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShanker%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20college%20right%20to%20grow%20mushroom%20spawns.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20huge%20market%20base%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20also%20abroad%20where%20he%20exports%20his%20produce%20to%20neighbouring%20countries%20including%20Bhutan%20and%20Nepal%2C%20and%20the%20UAE.%20Currently%2C%20his%20monthly%20revenue%20stands%20at%20Rs%2013%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMushrooming%20ideas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shanker%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20quit%20MBA%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20doubted%20my%20abilities%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20concentrate%20on%20shaping%20my%20career%20instead%20of%20running%20a%20business%20at%20this%20age.%20People%20from%20my%20caste%20are%20expected%20to%20become%20IAS%20officers.%20I%20was%20never%20interested%20in%20that.%20And%20to%20make%20it%20worse%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20college%20after%20the%20first%20semester%20mocking%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20after%20dropping%20out%20of%20college%2C%20Shanker%20tried%20his%20hands%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282454%2Fmother-son-duo-leenas-how-to-grow-mushroom-farm-earnings-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecul