to%202.25%20lakh%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20day.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Shouvik%20Dhar%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20obvious%20choice%20of%20hiring%20more%20people%20was%20there%20but%20Shouvik%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20something%20different.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20of%20hiring%20and%20training%20felt%20lengthy%20and%20repetitive%20to%20me%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20innovate%20something%20new.%20This%20set%20me%20on%20a%20quest%20to%20explore%20different%20types%20of%20machines%20used%20for%20making%20food%20items%20to%20eventually%20invent%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShouvik%20embarked%20on%20journeys%20to%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20Korea%20to%20study%20their%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CI%20discovered%20various%20machinery%2C%20reverse-engineered%20many%2C%20and%20ultimately%20developed%20my%20own%20%3Cem%3Emomo%3C%2Fem%3E-making%20machine.%20By%202018%2C%20the%20machine%20was%20up%20and%20running.%20Currently%2C%20our%20company%20operates%20entirely%20on%20automated%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20proudly%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20machine%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20the%20outer%20cover%20and%20the%20filling.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20the%20filling%20goes%20through%20a%20meticulous%20process%20from%20cutting%20to%20washing.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20take%20the%20example%20of%20a%20vegetable%20%3Cem%3Emomo%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20prepared.%20All%20the%20veggies%20arrive%20in%20the%20kitchen%20and%20then%20the%20cutting%20process%20is%20automated.%20Various%20machines%2C%20ranging%20from%20dicing%20to%20shredding%2C%20handle%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20automated%20cutting%2C%20the%20veggies%20are%20washed%20and%20transferred%20to%20a%20cooking%20wok.%20We%20use%20an%20automated%20cooking%20wok%20%E2%80%94%20a%20robotic%20wok%2C%20essentially%20%E2%80%94%20to%20cook%20the%20filling.%20Multiple%20woks%20are%20operated%20simultaneously%20to%20meet%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20phase%2C%20Shouvik%20explains%20that%20the%20focus%20shifts%20to%20dough%20processing%2C%20with%20the%20dough%20being%20prepared%20in%20a%20vacuum%20dough%20mixer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20specialised%20equipment%20that%20ensures%20even%20mixing%20by%20creating%20a%20vacuum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20dough%20and%20filling%20are%20prepared%2C%20the%20dough%20is%20fed%20into%20a%20forming%20machine%2C%20where%20it%20is%20taken%20in%2C%20and%20the%20filling%20is%20loaded%20onto%20a%20filling%20hopper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20machines%20work%20automatically%20to%20shape%20the%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Each%20production%20line%20consists%20of%20three%20different%20units%2C%20and%20each%20line%20can%20produce%20around%208%2C000%20pieces%20in%20an%20hour.%20Each%20machine%20can%20produce%202.25%20lakh%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eevery%20day.%20The%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecome%20out%20like%20on%20a%20conveyor%20belt%2C%20moving%20to%20the%20other%20end%20and%20entering%20the%20steamer.%20They%20are%20steamed%20for%20approximately%20four%20and%20a%20half%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20steaming%20process%2C%20the%20momos%20are%20placed%20in%20a%20pre-cooling%20chamber%20and%20then%20shock-frozen.%20This%20rapid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288148%2Frickshaw-puller-kissan-rural-innovation-food-processor-wins-national-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreezing%20process%20%3C%2Fa%3Eensures%20the%20preservation%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Once%20frozen%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20packed%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20about%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Zomoz%20makes%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eevery%20day%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20earning%20Rs%2025%20crore%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-2-1704806869.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shouvik%20is%20planning%20to%20open%2013%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20UAE.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-2-1704806869.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-2-1704806869-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-2-1704806869-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-2-1704806869-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-2-1704806869-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337841%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShouvik%20is%20planning%20to%20open%2013%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20UAE.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Shouvik%20Dhar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20makes%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eincluding%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20chicken%20and%20cheese%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20vegetable%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20paneer%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20crispy%20fried%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20more.%20Among%20these%2C%2065%20percent%20of%20the%20demand%20comes%20from%20chicken%20momos%2C%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYashika%20Rawat%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20of%20Zomoz%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20actually%20not%20made%20by%20a%20chef.%20%3Cem%3EMomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20by%20a%20fully%20automated%20machine%20sounds%20so%20absurd%20but%20I%20have%20to%20say%20that%20it%20tastes%20the%20same%2C%20or%20even%20better!%20My%20favourite%20is%20chicken%20and%20cheese%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20they%20always%20taste%20fresh.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20future%20plans%2C%20Shouvik%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTier%20two%20cities%2C%20known%20for%20their%20price%20sensitivity%20in%20comparison%20to%20tier%20one%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20have%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20promising%20market%20for%20us.%20Despite%20the%20price%20sensitivity%2C%20our%20outlets%20in%20tier-two%20cities%20have%20demonstrated%20significant%20success.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20or%20within%20the%20next%20year%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20further%20expand%20our%20presence%20in%20the%20existing%20cities%20and%20explore%20additional%20tier-two%20cities%20in%20proximity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20they%20have%20collaborated%20with%20another%20food%20business%20to%20open%2013%20outlets%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704809260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Realising%20that%20there%20were%20no%20good%20momo%20joints%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Zomoz%20founder%20Shouvik%20Dhar%20innovated%20an%20automated%20momo%20machine%20that%20can%20make%20lakhs%20of%20momos%20in%20a%20day!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337833%2Fzomoz-startup-nit-engineer-innovated-automated-momo-machine-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Child%20Labourer%20Rescued%20By%20Kailash%20Satyarthi%2C%20He%E2%80%99s%20Now%20a%20Lawyer%20Fighting%20For%20Rights%20of%20Hundreds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESix-year-old%20Amar%20Lal%20from%20Rajast